<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<a href="./PeteyLeinonen">PeteyLeinonen</a>: The first time I entered the top of Mount Doom I had three companion Nightwalkers. Every time I leave and come back to the top of Mount Doom, I get three new Nightwalker companions, with the same level and hitpoints as the original three that I entered Mount Doom with. I have managed to get nine simultaneous companions this way (I should only ever be able to have three companions if I create them the normal way), but I suspect I could get many more. <p>
<a href="./NeilStevens">NeilStevens</a>: Yes, this one will be tricky to address.  You can duplicate artifacts on Mount Doom, too. 
</p>
